# Echo — environment variables
#
# The importer + trend cache need NO secrets:
#   - Brand-voice import is 100% client-side (you upload a posts file you exported;
#     it's parsed in your browser). See docs/social-import-upload.md.
#   - Trends come from a local cache (Feature 1), not a paid per-request source.
#
# The two MODEL routes need a Google model provider — pick ONE of the two below:
#   - api/audit.js    (Suggestion Model / the audit) uses it when configured,
#                      else falls back to a templated mock — so it always answers.
#   - api/generate.js (Generation Model) REQUIRES it (no on-device fallback).
#
# Everything below is SERVER-ONLY. NEVER prefix a real secret with VITE_ — that
# ships it to the browser. Never paste secrets into chat or commits.

# --- Option 1: Gemini Developer API (simplest — a static key, no GCP setup) ---
# Get one at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey. Takes precedence over the Vertex
# vars below when set. NOTE: on the FREE tier Google may use your prompts to
# improve its models; use a billing-enabled (paid) key or Vertex to avoid that.
GEMINI_API_KEY=AQ.xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# --- Option 2: Vertex AI (service account — enterprise controls, zero retention) ---
# Needs a GCP service account (role: Vertex AI User), the Vertex AI API enabled,
# and billing active on the project. Used only when GEMINI_API_KEY is unset.
# GOOGLE_VERTEX_PROJECT=your-gcp-project-id
# GOOGLE_VERTEX_LOCATION=asia-south1   # region: asia-south1 (Mumbai) / us-central1 / global
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_EMAIL=svc-account@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
# GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"

# --- Optional model overrides (Vertex "google/<model>" form; normalized per provider) ---
# ECHO_MODEL=google/gemini-2.5-flash            # default for both routes
# ECHO_AUDIT_MODEL=google/gemini-2.5-flash      # Suggestion Model only
# ECHO_GENERATE_MODEL=google/gemini-2.5-pro     # Generation Model only

# --- OpenRouter (still used by carousel slide images, /api/normalise, /api/voice) ---
# Optional. Without it those degrade gracefully (e.g. carousel ships without AI art).
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
